name: getWebhookDeliveries
description: Lists webhook_deliveries for the authenticated user

filter[status][eq].description: Return only webhook_deliveries matching the given `status`

filter[webhook][contains].description: Return only webhook deliveries whose `webhook` component contains the given text

filter[attempts][contains].description: Return only webhook_deliveries whose `attempts` component contains the given text

filter[started_at][gte].description: Return only webhook_deliveries whose delivery started later than or at given ISO 8601 datetime

filter[started_at][lte].description: Return only webhook_deliveries whose delivery started earlier than or at given ISO 8601 datetime

filter[finished_at][gte].description: Return only webhook_deliveries whose delivery finished later than or at given ISO 8601 datetime

filter[finished_at][lte].description: Return only webhook_deliveries whose delivery finished earlier than or at given ISO 8601 datetime
